cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a novel approach for training generative models and encoders using adversarial criterion. This is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision, which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper emphasizes the importance of semantic representation of data, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
